  "subject": "Fix message-router connection error handling",
  "commit_message": "Fix message-router connection error handling\n\nOnce the message-router connection error occurred, htbtworker\nsubprocess was terminated by the error and notification polling\nstopped.\nThis change adds an error handling so that the polling process\ncan continue working even if dmaap is temporarily down.\n\nSigned-off-by: Satoshi Fujii <fujii-satoshi@jp.fujitsu.com>\nIssue-ID: DCAEGEN2-2952\nChange-Id: Idbc096895a58af9944b68ee0808e1ea895d2e2cd\n",
